title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Start from scratch Airbus H135 helicopter
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can start the Airbus H135 helicopter from scratch. We will look at almost every button in the helicopter so sit back and relax.

You can download the  Airbus H135 from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/discover/helicopter

Keep in mind this aircraft it not compatible with the A32NX mod currently.
